Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.74,0:25:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.06,0:25:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,CLARKSON: I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.66,0:25:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry, I am so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.94,0:25:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.18,0:26:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you. \N- Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.14,0:26:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry, chaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.66,0:26:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And what makes it worse is the chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.42,0:26:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Top Gear Dog has eaten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.72,0:26:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a disaster, but
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.30,0:26:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,ladies and gentlemen,\Na big hand for Supergrass!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.22,0:26:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.54,0:26:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.86,0:26:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.26,0:26:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier on, we asked McFly\Nif they could write a song
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.82,0:26:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,before the end of the show,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.26,0:26:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,including the words Sofa,\NAdministration and Hyundai.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.22,0:26:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to see how they got on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.70,0:26:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would like to hear the McFly's\N"{\i1}Sofa, Administration and Hyundai{\i0}"?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.26,0:26:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, play it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.92,0:26:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.54,0:26:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go, ready?
