Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.58,0:28:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.74,0:28:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you.\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.98,0:28:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That was brilliant, and\Nnow we're going to do
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.06,0:28:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,something that almost certainly...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.06,0:28:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,won't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.18,0:28:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because we're going\Nto play us out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.46,0:28:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on bass.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.70,0:28:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time I played one\Nof these, I broke it... on the singer,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.50,0:28:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and that was about 20 years ago,\Nso I might be a bit rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.34,0:28:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I have to say,\Nmy piano that I've got at home
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.50,0:28:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't have all these switches\Nand knobs on it, and I normally use it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.82,0:28:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to play things like Bach and Beethoven,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.50,0:28:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but Jeremy wants us to do\Nsomething by a Billy Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.50,0:28:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.66,0:28:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided we're going to do\N"Red Light Spells Danger", because
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.18,0:28:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I listened to it, and apart from a couple\Nof twiddly bits I'm a bit nervous about,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.58,0:28:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,, I reckon it's okay for someone\Nwho's only had seven lessons.
